<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF7A6AC5FCE4910C1DB5BCDF" pageId="129" pageNumber="888" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF7A6AC5FCE4910C1DB5BCDF" blockId="129.[791,1383,1798,2225]" pageId="129" pageNumber="888">
Based on multivariate analyses of forearm and cranial measurements, S. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF7A6AC5FB0391D81B67BCAC" authorityName="Milne-Edwards" authorityYear="1881" box="[1279,1383,1921,1950]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Scotophilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="129" pageNumber="888" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="robustus">robustus</taxonomicName>
is distinct from 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF7A6AC5FBEF91FD1A80BCF7" baseAuthorityName="A. Smith" baseAuthorityYear="1833" box="[1043,1152,1956,1989]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Scotophilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="129" pageNumber="888" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="dinganii">dinganii</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF7A6AC5FB2791FD1B61BCF7" baseAuthorityName="E. Geoffroy" baseAuthorityYear="1803" box="[1243,1377,1956,1989]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Scotophilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="129" pageNumber="888" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="borbonicus">borbonicus</taxonomicName>
. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
